About 74 Jarrett Dr

  • Rental income
  • Mountain view
  • Short term rental
Meet a rare opportunity to own 1 acre of land in the heart of the Ledger community. With mountain views, this property is ready for your vision—whether it's building your dream home, creating a short-term rental retreat, or simply holding onto a beautiful slice of Western North Carolina. The existing home on the property needs to be removed, but the true value lies in the unrestricted land—offering endless possibilities with no zoning limitations. Enjoy peaceful surroundings, year-round views, and the convenience of being just minutes from Bakersville, Spruce Pine, the Blue Ridge Parkway, or the Appalachian Trail. The Middle and High School for the county are about .5 a mile away.
Listing Agent - Kelly Pittman Jones; Listing Agent Contact: Kelly@properrealty.net; Listing Office - Proper Realty LLC, MLS#4284829 last updated 4 hours ago. Movoto checked Canopy MLS for data 30 minutes ago.
